Description:
    Adds a staging environment.  Basically a production environment with logging (config.log_level set to true)

Example:
    rails generate add_staging_env env_name

    Arguments:
      env_name the name of the environment you wish to use for staging
    Creates:
      * config/environments/env_name.rb
      * spec/controllers/pages_controller_spec.rb (
    Injects Into:
      * config/database.yml
    Gems:
      * depends on shoulda for testing, which it adds in if it isn't in the Gemfile
    Dependencies:
      * high_voltage, rspec, shoulda
    Expects:
      * devise test helpers must be defined for rspec, preferably in spec/support/devise.rb